author: Clayton Purdom
title: Newswire: May we all endure the Oscars with the dignity of Jackie Chan
text:
Share Tweet 
The Oscars have begun with a rousing performance by Justin Timberlake of “ Can’t Stop The Feeling ,” his Oscar-nominated song from the Trolls movie. While many celebrities were visibly struggling to enjoy themselves throughout the performance, only one had to do so while apparently standing directly adjacent to the entrance: Jackie Chan. May we all suffer our indignities, as he did this one.
